PrecisREGISTRATION OF STORAGE TANK SYSTEMS FOR PETROLEUM PRODUCTS AND ALLIED PETROLEUM PRODUCTS ON FEDERAL LANDS REGULATIONS which will require all underground and large surface petroleum storage tank systems (more than 4,000 litres) located on federal property be registered with the department or agency responsible for its administration.
